---
// StateMetrics.astro — Pure CSS animated metrics comparing chains vs loops
// Animated bar charts and stat cards
---

<div class="sm-wrap">
  <h3 class="sm-title">Chains vs Loops — The Numbers</h3>
  <p class="sm-sub">What changes when you replace sequential chains with stateful loops.</p>

  <!-- Stat cards -->
  <div class="sm-grid">
    <div class="sm-card sm-card--green">
      <div class="sm-icon">🔄</div>
      <div class="sm-value sm-value--green">3<span class="sm-unit">×</span></div>
      <div class="sm-label">Fewer Crashed<br/>Workflows</div>
    </div>
    <div class="sm-card sm-card--cyan">
      <div class="sm-icon">🧩</div>
      <div class="sm-value sm-value--cyan">100<span class="sm-unit">%</span></div>
      <div class="sm-label">State Visible<br/>at Every Step</div>
    </div>
    <div class="sm-card sm-card--amber">
      <div class="sm-icon">🧪</div>
      <div class="sm-value sm-value--amber">1<span class="sm-unit">fn</span></div>
      <div class="sm-label">Each Node<br/>Tested Alone</div>
    </div>
    <div class="sm-card sm-card--purple">
      <div class="sm-icon">↻</div>
      <div class="sm-value sm-value--purple">∞<span class="sm-unit"></span></div>
      <div class="sm-label">Loop Back<br/>When Needed</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Comparison bars -->
  <div class="sm-comparison">
    <div class="sm-comp-title">Error Recovery: Chain vs Loop</div>

    <div class="sm-bar-group">
      <div class="sm-bar-label">
        <span class="sm-bar-icon">⛓</span>
        <span class="sm-bar-name sm-bar-name--red">CHAIN</span>
        <span class="sm-bar-val">Crash. Restart from scratch.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="sm-bar-track">
        <div class="sm-bar-fill sm-bar-fill--red" style="--target-width: 100%"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="sm-bar-group">
      <div class="sm-bar-label">
        <span class="sm-bar-icon">🔄</span>
        <span class="sm-bar-name sm-bar-name--green">LOOP</span>
        <span class="sm-bar-val">Re-route. Keep state. Continue.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="sm-bar-track">
        <div class="sm-bar-fill sm-bar-fill--green" style="--target-width: 25%"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="sm-savings">
      <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" class="sm-savings-icon"><path d="M10 2 L18 10 L14 10 L14 18 L6 18 L6 10 L2 10 Z" fill="#4ade80" transform="rotate(180,10,10)" opacity="0.6"/></svg>
      <span>Loops preserve state across errors. No lost work, no full restarts.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Debugging comparison -->
  <div class="sm-comparison">
    <div class="sm-comp-title">Debugging: Chain vs Loop</div>

    <div class="sm-bar-group">
      <div class="sm-bar-label">
        <span class="sm-bar-icon">⛓</span>
        <span class="sm-bar-name sm-bar-name--red">CHAIN</span>
        <span class="sm-bar-val">Print statements. Prayer.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="sm-bar-track">
        <div class="sm-bar-fill sm-bar-fill--red" style="--target-width: 90%"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="sm-bar-group">
      <div class="sm-bar-label">
        <span class="sm-bar-icon">🔄</span>
        <span class="sm-bar-name sm-bar-name--green">LOOP</span>
        <span class="sm-bar-val">State snapshots. Replay any node.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="sm-bar-track">
        <div class="sm-bar-fill sm-bar-fill--green" style="--target-width: 20%"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="sm-savings">
      <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" class="sm-savings-icon"><path d="M10 2 L18 10 L14 10 L14 18 L6 18 L6 10 L2 10 Z" fill="#818cf8" transform="rotate(180,10,10)" opacity="0.6"/></svg>
      <span>With state snapshots, you can replay the exact input to any node and see what went wrong.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .sm-wrap {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%);
    border-radius: 16px; padding: 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; border: 1px solid #334155;
  }
  .sm-title { color: #f1f5f9; font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 0.25rem; }
  .sm-sub { color: #64748b; font-size: 0.8rem; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; font-family: monospace; }

  .sm-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) { .sm-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }

  .sm-card {
    text-align: center; padding: 16px 8px; border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid #334155; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    transition: transform 0.2s, border-color 0.3s;
  }
  .sm-card:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); }
  .sm-card--green:hover { border-color: #4ade8040; }
  .sm-card--cyan:hover { border-color: #06b6d440; }
  .sm-card--amber:hover { border-color: #f59e0b40; }
  .sm-card--purple:hover { border-color: #818cf840; }

  .sm-icon { font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .sm-value {
    font-family: monospace; font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 6px;
    animation: sm-count 1.5s ease-out;
  }
  .sm-value--green { color: #4ade80; text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(74,222,128,0.3); }
  .sm-value--cyan { color: #06b6d4; text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(6,182,212,0.3); }
  .sm-value--amber { color: #f59e0b; text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(245,158,11,0.3); }
  .sm-value--purple { color: #818cf8; text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(129,140,248,0.3); }
  .sm-unit { font-size: 1rem; opacity: 0.7; }
  .sm-label { font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.55rem; color: #64748b; line-height: 1.4; }
  @keyframes sm-count { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }

  .sm-comparison {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.25); border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .sm-comp-title {
    font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.7rem; color: #64748b;
    margin-bottom: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }
  .sm-bar-group { margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .sm-bar-label { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; margin-bottom: 5px; }
  .sm-bar-icon { font-size: 0.8rem; }
  .sm-bar-name { font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 700; }
  .sm-bar-name--red { color: #f87171; }
  .sm-bar-name--green { color: #4ade80; }
  .sm-bar-val { font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.6rem; color: #64748b; margin-left: auto; }

  .sm-bar-track { height: 20px; background: #1e293b; border-radius: 6px; overflow: hidden; }
  .sm-bar-fill {
    height: 100%; border-radius: 6px; width: 0%;
    animation: sm-bar-grow 1.8s ease-out forwards; animation-delay: 0.3s;
  }
  .sm-bar-fill--red { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ef4444, #f87171); }
  .sm-bar-fill--green { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #22c55e, #4ade80); animation-delay: 0.6s; }
  @keyframes sm-bar-grow { to { width: var(--target-width); } }

  .sm-savings {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 12px; padding-top: 10px; border-top: 1px solid #334155;
    font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.7rem; color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .sm-savings-icon { flex-shrink: 0; }
</style>
